remarks: Cicadas were loud. Hard to hear bird song. Detected OVEN and WOTH within 30 seconds of leaving point.
Plot was plowed yesterday after I surveyed it. No grass left, just plowed dirt. Amazing number of Yellow-billed Cuckoos! Hears/saw from both sides of the field.
62 dB background noise Kestrel device showed between 99.7 - 99.9 for RH%
